name: Violin has transcended the du rag on a mushroom trip 004
description:
4/4 series: violin, spraypaint, acrylic pour, gold chains, photography, digital manipulation
______

Violin transcends all its identities and becomes love, the frequency of music, after a peacefully gnarly trip into the body. Nothing mens anything because everything is everything.


*******
Violin represents artist, Jasminfire, who experienced a love-hate relationship with the instrument. The colors, du-rag and chains represent several identities she created around being a violinist as a defense mechanism for dealing with social anxiety and difficulty connecting with others outside of a music space.
